    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="intro">
  <div class="container intro__content">
    <h2 class="section-heading">Training That Fits</h2>
    <p>
      Whether you're returning to fitness, building from the ground up, or adding strength to your running or cycling routine, we meet you where you are and build from there.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our sessions are built around movement — not numbers — focusing on technique, control, and the kind of strength that carries over to everyday life.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

