  <div class="container audience__grid">
    <div class="audience__card">
      <h3>New to Strength Training</h3>
      <p>Start with confidence. Learn the movements and build a foundation without pressure.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="audience__card">
      <h3>Endurance Athletes</h3>
      <p>Add strength work that supports your running or cycling, improving resilience and reducing injury risk.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="audience__card">
      <h3>Long-Term Clients</h3>
      <p>Build a practice that lasts. Many of our clients train with us for years — not weeks.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

